title: Coolest Husband Ever
description:
Mike's got his wife wrapped around his little finger.

* Watch a special filmed version of this sketch here: http://youtu.be/Y8p8_iPb7Ng *

Starring Lisa Kleinman, Avery Monsen, Dan Hodapp, and Jonathan Marballi
Written by Jon Bershad
Directed by Jim Santangeli
Shot and Edited by Alex Adan

Taped on January 30th, 2012
